o achieve a better quality of life and become less of a burden on the system. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">There is evidence that</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">even the most challenged patients can be encouraged to manage actively.</span><a name="_ftnref5"></a><a href="#_ftn5">[5]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Over the past </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">20 </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">year</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Arthritis Care </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ha</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> delivered over 100</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">0’s of</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> self-management training courses. We feel that we can bring our experience of working with people on self–management to bear to help shape</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> and deliver</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">SSM elements of the</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> strategy.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-